---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="Ambassador" sideBarActiveItemID="ambassador">
  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">Zesh Elizabeth</div>
  </div>
  <Image
    src="/ambassador.png"
    class="w-full"
    alt="ambassador"
    width="1200"
    height="1200"
  />
  <div class="grow w-full flex-col md:flex-row">
    <p class="py-1 text-1xl">
      Meet ..... the vibrant Art Ambassador of iLLUMINANZZ!
    </p>
    <p class="py-1 text-1xl">
      From mastering Indian classical dance since the tender age of 3 to
      choreographing captivating performances for children at just 8 years old,
      Zesh's journey through the world of arts has been nothing short of
      extraordinary.
    </p>
    <p class="py-1 text-1xl">
      Not only is Zesh a winner of the prestigious Viva inter school dance fest
      organized by Vibgyor High, but also a talented swimmer and football
      champion. In academics, Zesh shines just as brightly, emerging as the
      topper in ISC commerce and currently pursuing studies in business along
      with chartered management accounting.
    </p>
    <p class="py-1 text-1xl">
      Despite the rigors of academia, Zesh's passion for Latin dance remains
      undimmed, making waves in the dance community with skillful moves and
      infectious enthusiasm. Beyond the stage and classroom, Zesh is a
      captivating speaker, earning accolades and victories in competitions while
      also excelling in theatre arts. From portraying witches to angels, Zesh's
      performances leave audiences spellbound, showcasing a remarkable talent
      for bringing characters to life.
    </p>
    <p class="py-1 text-1xl">
      Adding to her list of achievements, Zesh also represents her college union
      as General Secretary, demonstrating exceptional leadership and
      organizational skills. With a diverse array of talents and a boundless
      passion for the arts, Zesh truly embodies the spirit of creativity and
      excellence.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
